    dc:description "Fig. 29. A–C. Bruceina areneformis sp. nov., holotype, height 4.3 mm (MNHN-IM-2000-35699). D–F. Carinastele achrosta sp. nov., holotype, height 8.7 mm (MNHN-IM-2000-35705). G–H. Portions of the above holotypes to illustrate numbering of spiral cords, following Marshall (1988). G. Bruceina areneformis sp. nov.H. Carinastele achrosta sp. nov. The equivalent of P2 is not present inB. areneformis sp. nov." ;
